column2: SELECT m.name, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,   p.objid AS sdssid, p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2,    n.distance,    p.g, p.r, p.PetroRad_g AS radiusg, p.PetroRad_r as radiusr,   sm.logMass as mass into mydb.output_table4 from MyDB.Void_Dwarfs AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.RA, m.DEC, #) AS n   JOIN photoObj AS p ON p.objid = n.objid   JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid   JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS sm on sm.specobjid = s.specobjid    AND s.Class = &&&
